    <string name="onboarding_p1_title">Yachaq yanapay bolsillollaykipi</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p1_body">Mira huk qhaway llank\'ana, cuello uterino siq\'ita qhawan qanwan kuska, hinaspataq nin paciente kachayta munanchuchus chayta. Qan kachkanki kamachiyniyuq.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p2_title">Kimsa atinalla ruway</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p2_body">Pacienteta wakichiy hinaspa huk kutilla ñit\'iy. Mira utqayllata kimsa siq\'ita hurqun, aswan sumaqta akllan, hinaspataq qhawayta qhawachisunki nisqa qillqayuqta. Qan kamachinki imatachus ruwanaykita.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p3_title">Pakasqa willanaykiqa ñawpaq</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p3_body">Pacientekunaq siq\'inkunaqa kay celularpi qhipanqanku. Mira manapuni kachkachinmanchu mayman akllaspaykiwanchu.</string>
